Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.91,0:22:45.88,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:50.01,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Comparing Heights
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:48.45,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Comparing Heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:53.51,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Behold, Asta! See how much I've grown!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.76,0:22:58.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean, I've grown, too, \Nmaybe, I think, somewhat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.72,0:23:02.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If you look closer, I think you'll \Nsee we're about the same height!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:06.03,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be foolish! Then let \Nus compare our heights!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.03,0:23:07.74,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,See? I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:11.72,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:13.32,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I must help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:19.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,See? We {\i1}are{\i0} about the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:20.29,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,But that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.59,0:23:22.79,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:25.29,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm at it, I'll just let you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:31.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that, Leo!\N I'm taller than you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:35.81,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, even I would notice this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.57,0:23:42.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Leo! Who said you could grow without me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.16,0:23:43.61,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it has been six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:47.30,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I've also grown these six... \NHey! Just where are you looking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:23:48.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.35,0:23:53.55,main,Some,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 159: \N"Quiet Lakes and Forest Shadows."
